History 
Jonathan Bell Lovelace believed that fundamental research is essential to achieving superior long-term investment results. The small company he founded in 1931 has grown into one of the world’s most respected financial institutions.



















Management Team 
Our governance structure is built on the premise that a group of individuals with diverse perspectives can reach better decisions through discussion and debate.



















Company Culture 
In an environment where great ideas are allowed to flourish, our associates are bound by a common purpose and a shared set of values.









Office Locations
News Room












 




































Our Services














The entire Capital Group organization is aligned behind one mission: Deliver superior, long-term investment results and service.
Learn more about our approach.













 







 Institutions & Consultants 




















Corporations, governments, pension and retirement plans, and nonprofit organizations rely on us to protect and grow their assets. We offer equity, fixed-income and balanced investment portfolios through separately managed accounts and pooled funds.

+ View regions



  
 Asia (ex. Japan) 
 Australia & New Zealand 
 Canada 
 Europe 
 Japan 
  
  
 United States 
 







 
 













 







 Financial Advisors & Intermediaries 




















We provide practice management and investment services to help financial advisors and intermediaries develop highly effective solutions and portfolios for their clients.

+ View regions



  
 Australia & New Zealand 
 Canada 
 Europe 
 Japan 
  
 United States 
 







 
 













 







 Individual Investors 




















We help millions of individual investors around the world meet their financial goals. We are the home of American Funds in the U.S., and also offer investment funds and mutual funds in Australia, Canada, Europe and Japan.

+ View regions



 Canada 
 Europe 
 Hong Kong 
 Japan 
 Singapore 
 United States 
 







 
 













 







 High-Net-Worth Investors 




















Since 1974, we have cultivated relationships with high-net-worth clients that span generations. Through Capital Group Private Client Services we offer investment and trust services for wealthy individuals and families, nonprofits and private foundations.

+ View regions



 United States 
 







 
 


























